Package: fresh
Title: FWA-Referenced Spatial Hydrology
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Allan", "Irvine", , "al@newgraphenvironment.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3495-2128")),
    person("New Graph Environment", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Stream network-aware spatial operations via direct SQL against
    fwapg and bcfishpass. Snap points to streams, delineate watersheds, query
    fish observations, and fetch network-referenced lakes, wetlands, and
    streams from the BC Freshwater Atlas. Requires PostgreSQL with fwapg,
    bcfishpass, and bcfishobs.
